data.description: Welcome to your new home! This charming 3 bed, 2 bath residence is move-in ready, offering not just a house but a lifestyle. The open and airy floor plan creates a welcoming atmosphere, ideal for both everyday living and entertaining guests. The kitchen is equipped with modern stainless steel appliances. The three bedrooms are generously sized, providing private retreats for every member of the household. The two bathrooms are thoughtfully designed, ensuring convenience and functionality for the busy routines of daily life. Step outside into the expansive yard—a canvas for your outdoor dreams. Whether you envision lively gatherings, serene evenings under the stars, or a play haven for children and pets, this large yard offers endless possibilities. And for those with a green thumb, there's ample space to cultivate a garden of your own. But that's not all; this property comes complete with a storage shed, offering a solution for all your organizational needs. Whether you're a hobbyist, gardener, or simply in need of extra space, the storage shed provides a practical and tidy solution. Conveniently located and move-in ready, this home is not just a dwelling; it's an opportunity to create lasting memories. Don't miss out on the chance to make this residence your own. Schedule a viewing today and discover the endless potential that this 3 bed, 2 bath home with a large yard and storage shed has to offer!
